        "text": "Washington gentlemen, I was afraid & for we were so clo\nwas with Germany then. I mailed them from Tulsa, so of\nmight have heard of this happening at that time. We know\nthat dream of 3 nights did not then come true. But the\nis still time that something very similar may yet happ\nEnclosed is postage for mailing this to the pro\nyou know will consider it from a serious possibility and\nalso a rough sketch that I've made, my idea of Russian\nmethod. I would appreciate hearing your opinion\non the above scientific possibility mentioned. I know noth\nof science actually. I am Sincerely yours.\nWish I did."
